
// Text on first line with indented continuation
barista: Hey, how are you?
  Anything to drink?

// Multiple continuation lines
barista: Welcome to the café!
  We have espresso, latte, and cappuccino.
  What can I get you?

// Tag + inline text + continuation
barista: <friendly> Hey there!
  Good to see you again.

// Interpolation on first line + continuation
state
  drink: latte

barista: Today's special: $drink.
  Highly recommended!

// Non-continuation: next line at same indent stays separate
barista: Just one line here.

barista: And another single line.

/*
<test>
- expected: |
    barista:
      Hey, how are you?
      Anything to drink?

    barista:
      Welcome to the café!
      We have espresso, latte, and cappuccino.
      What can I get you?

    barista:
      <<friendly>>Hey there!
      Good to see you again.

    barista:
      Today's special: latte.
      Highly recommended!

    barista: Just one line here.

    barista: And another single line.
</test>
*/
